11#include "rtc_base/net_helper.h"
12
13namespace cricket {
14
15const char UDP_PROTOCOL_NAME[] = "udp";
16const char TCP_PROTOCOL_NAME[] = "tcp";
17const char SSLTCP_PROTOCOL_NAME[] = "ssltcp";
18const char TLS_PROTOCOL_NAME[] = "tls";
19
20int GetProtocolOverhead(const std::string& protocol) {
21 if (protocol == TCP_PROTOCOL_NAME || protocol == SSLTCP_PROTOCOL_NAME) {
22 return kTcpHeaderSize;
23 } else if (protocol == UDP_PROTOCOL_NAME) {
24 return kUdpHeaderSize;
25 } else {
26 // TODO(srte): We should crash on unexpected input and handle TLS correctly.
27 return 8;
28 }
29}
30
31} // namespace cricket
